snippet.textDisplay: All we have is each other . Nothing else on this earth matters. Money, success, fame, it can come and go and its not fun,  but nothing can lift you off your feet , or bring you truly to your knees,  than another human being. We are to each other what gives all this any meaning. Everything  is nothing if you dont have anyone to share it with.   Slow down and dont rush   . Take your time with people and be all in. Be accepting and welcoming of people and their imperfections,  and be kind enough and willing to give yourself and expose your own imperfections. Because in all those imperfections you'll look back one day and see perfection. I think everyone could agree that if there is only one true thing we all feel eventually is that we wish we  could go back and just love more . I hope he finds peace.  You're not alone brother. We all fall short.   Forgive yourself .  Because you are worth forgiving.
